headline: BCU Strengthens Jack Henry Relationship to Support Growth Goals
summary: Jack Henry™ (Nasdaq: JKHY) announced today that BCU is continuing its long-standing relationship with the company, leveraging Jack Henry's cloud-based platform to support its long-term growth and commitment to delivering strong member service.
